ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T23:23:46.000Z","msg":"如果站務台可以，同一題目可否 set 定同一日唔超過3個，以免五毛洗版？又或者行動 po 自動排上熱門？<br />\n大家討論吓點可以抗衡五毛入侵，帶風向問題。"},{"pid":"b3e57f0ed6c65b10f80a65386d08327e2d7fe64d","tid":1675737,"uid":74598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T00:40:42.000Z","msg":"咁"},{"pid":"839a92b6c76cb0fb7b2af99c9edaa2d9309edc52","tid":1675737,"uid":159755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T00:48:38.000Z","msg":"分析得有道理 特別係第三點"},{"pid":"8c1323e9b71e6fb00142aed1c7c72d79b5e485e4","tid":1675737,"uid":146434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T01:14:09.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n食爆黃店 唔好集中龍門冰室<br />\n好多黃色小店要人"}]}